Ginga: "Yui, I'm sorry for keeping silent until now..."
01_優衣_戦闘冷たい目
Yui: "It's okay..."
Yui: "Even without using such magic, I'll show that I can win."
Yui: "Even if you two are willing, my feelings won't change."

Yui: "Standing here, frightened and doing nothing... that would be a
disgrace to a hero."
Yui: "I'm going."
01_優衣_ピンチB
01_男主人公_A
Ginga: "I won't let you go!"

Ginga: "Leave the rest to the police. Yui, you've already fought
enough... everyone in town thinks so too!"
Yui: "No..."

Yui: "Of course, it's for the peace of the town... but it's also for
my own happiness."
Yui: "I want... I want to hear Ginga's cheerful voice."

Yui: "I want to talk about silly things with Ginga as usual and
laugh."

Yui: "There's no future like that in a world ruled by Zaida-G. That's
why I'm going!"

Yui: "You see, I wanted Ginga to cheer for me... If Ginga feels the
same way, that alone gives me courage."
Ginga: "Yui..."
Ginga: "But without the ultimate magic, we can't defeat Da-Gunoa."
Yui: "We won't know unless we try!"
Yui: "The source of holy power is the power of love..."
Yui: "If Ginga cheers for me, then even miracles..."
Ginga: "..."
Yui: "Let me fight Da-Gunoa once more!"
Yui: "...Please, Ginga, let me go!"
Ginga: "Yui..."

Ginga: "...Seriously, you never listen once you've made up your mind,
do you?"
Yui: "Ginga..."
Ginga: "Polka, is it okay to do as Yui says?"
01_ポルカ_A
Polka: "Ginga, do you understand what that means...?"
Ginga: "Yes, I understand."
Polka: "..."
Polka: "..."
Polka: "...Alright then."
Polka: "I'll take a chance on the two of you as well."
Ginga: "Yui, but there's a condition. Will you listen?"
01_優衣_何
Yui: "A condition...?"

Ginga: "As Polka said, without the ultimate magic, Da-Gunoa can't be
sealed."

Ginga: "But it's not okay to use the ultimate magic at the cost of
Yui's life."
Ginga: "So..."
Ginga: "The Holy Resurrection will be chanted by both me and Yui."
Yui & Polka: "What!?"

Ginga: "If both Yui and I chant it together, maybe it won't cost us
our lives."
01_優衣_ピンチB

Yui: "No! We can't take such a dangerous gamble. I don't want to put
Ginga in danger anymore."
Ginga: "Doesn't my feeling matter at all!?"
Yui: "Ginga..."
Ginga: "I said we'd die together, didn't I!?"
Ginga: "But I don't plan to die, not even a bit!"
Ginga: "I want to live and walk into the future with Yui."

Ginga: "I will never leave Yui alone. Trust me again, rely on me once
more!"
